{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" is the adapter between RevenueCat’s SDK and Swidux’s purchase-agnostic paywall plugin. The plugin owns paywall state (presentation flags, current entitlement, async progress); this package translates RevenueCat’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerInfo"},{"type":"text","text":" into the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot"},{"text":" the plugin expects, and surfaces the live ","type":"text"},{"code":"customerInfoStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so entitlement changes propagate without polling."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Two products ship together:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" — "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"text":" (the live ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" conformer) and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" (a controllable preview \/ test conformer)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallSheet"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterSheet"},{"type":"text","text":", drop-in SwiftUI views that wrap RevenueCatUI with platform-aware presentation, plus a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall(state:send:)"},{"type":"text","text":" view modifier that composes both."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The flow:"}]},{"code":["View → store.send(.paywall(.request(reason:)))","  → PaywallPlugin sets isPresented = true","  → PaywallSheet observes the change, presents RevenueCatUI.PaywallView","  → user purchases → Purchases.shared.customerInfoStream yields a new CustomerInfo","  → RevenueCatPaywallService maps it to EntitlementSnapshot","  → PaywallPlugin reduces .customerInfoUpdated, sets isPro = true","  → store.paywall.isGateSatisfied flips, gated UI unlocks"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The plugin and the adapter stay decoupled: the plugin doesn’t know about RevenueCat, and the adapter doesn’t know about your action tree."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Framework","title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","symbolKind":"module","modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"role":"collection","externalID":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallPlugin"},{"type":"text","text":". Implements "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" against "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":", ships a controllable mock for previews and tests, and pairs with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" for drop-in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterView"},{"type":"text","text":" presentation."}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Quickstart","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/GettingStarted"],